overview: Coronation! Talk about the Crown Jewels… London and most of the United Kingdom are certainly in the grip of a huge celebration. After a long reign it’s time to anoint a few new member or in our case a few big members. With a brand new cast and some proper fit British classic Triga lads some who without doubt are getting “Royally Crowned and anointed…with a faceful of unholy spunk…” this 155 min film has two absolutely banging hardcore scenes! These fitties are definitely getting more than a juicy fat big Orb and Sceptre stuck up his arse and lots of other places!  This is one class film in proper Triga tradition. Let the ride begin.
title: Coronation - The Yoof of Today
